Physical Design Rules/Constraints of spLOC variable-volume-mixer 

In order for this design to function you need:
    -gas permeable membrane vents for gas purging following mixing
    -open sensor window for mix measurments 
    -light sensor 
    -programable controller (can be closed loop or open loop system) for full automation and execution of protocols on this device 
        > see https://link.springer.com/content/pdf/10.1007/s10404-013-1180-2.pdf page 650 for details